Feature: : LogoutFunctionality
  As a user of the E-commerce application
  I want to be able to logout into my account
  so that I can access personalised features make purchases

  Scenario: Successful logout
    Given I am on the logout page
    When I enter valid username and password
    And I click on the login button
    When I click on account page
    And I click on logout button
    Then I should be redirected to the home page logout